      "body": "- When a follow up occurs, the pull request should be turned into a draft.\r\n- If it is already a draft, only leave the follow up message.[^01^] \r\n- When a disqualification occurs, the pull request should be closed. \r\n\r\nContext: https://github.com/ubiquity-os/plugins-wishlist/issues/60#issuecomment-2516409360\r\n\r\nRationale: when a contributor converts from draft to ready, then that signals it is ready for review. \n\n[^01^]: ⚠ 52% possible duplicate - [Reviewer Follow Ups](https://www.github.com/ubiquity-os-marketplace/daemon-disqualifier/issues/49#49)\n\n",
