      "active_lock_reason": null,
      "body": "This is the [issue](https://github.com/ubiquity-os/ubiquity-os-kernel/issues/166) where I got disqualified 3 days earlier than the deadline\r\n\r\nWhen I started the task with `/start` on 28th October, the bot said the deadline is Sat, Nov 2, 2:36 PM UTC, however on 30th October, the bot said the deadline has passed and unassigned me\r\n\r\nFound another [issue](https://github.com/ubiquity-os/permit-generation/issues/71#issuecomment-2448881918) with the same problem\r\n",
