      "body": "When no `KERNEL_PUBLIC_KEY` is supplied, the runs fail saying the given key is too short. My suspicion is that the default key is not used but `\"\"` is used instead. See this run for reference: https://github.com/ubiquity-os-marketplace/daemon-pricing/actions/runs/12128570532/job/33815214041\r\n\r\nSDKs will need to get updated across plugins as well.",
